cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.NE

The paper discusses multi-agent reinforcement learning (MARL) and evolutionary theory, which are both subfields of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also introduces an innovative modular architecture for deep reinforcement learning agents, which falls under the category of control systems and robotics (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the emergence of cooperative behavior amongst self-interested individuals, which is related to game theory and mechanism design (cs.MA). Finally, the paper presents results in two challenging environments, which suggests a focus on neural networks and optimization (cs.NE).
